# GauNidhi – Account Deletion Request

If you would like to delete or deactivate your **GauNidhi** account and all associated data, please send an email to **arthurfiddich@gmail.com** from your registered phone number or include your registered phone number in the email.

Our support team will review and verify your request.  
Account deactivation and permanent data deletion will be completed within **3–4 business days** of receiving the request.

---

## Data That Will Be Deleted
- Registered phone number
- Profile information
- Any user-provided or stored account data related to GauNidhi

---

## Data That May Be Retained
Some **anonymous analytics or security logs** may be retained for legal, fraud-prevention, or compliance purposes. These logs do not personally identify users.

---

## Contact
For any questions or assistance regarding your account or data, please contact:

**Email:** arthurfiddich@gmail.com

